有個second low 都夠啦"},{"pid":"6670ff60ad98b57e98b41c65240aa06492552aeb","tid":2065772,"uid":342115,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:54:08.000Z","msg":"死捱爛捱捱埋嗰一年 拎咗張畢業證書先 之後想做文人就再讀多個 咁樣貿貿然放棄三年嘅努力 有啲唔抵 你仲要唔係100%肯定讀到/啱讀新嗰科"},{"pid":"757ebcce09894471fdc7ecc8405cd9ea435f1497","tid":2065772,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:03:40.000Z","msg":"唔知樓主咩情況，但除非你好有錢，唔係真係要考慮下quit對你前途嘅影響"},{"pid":"826cfd689adc464382fa19a3b76eef40f6930b23","tid":2065772,"uid":213939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66138c8da815a3e268672070bd10952f271d03c3","tid":2065772,"uid":172051,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"8670de0232084f1a0c35a769473fc6edabbb05bd","tid":2065772,"uid":355064,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"4950ec66209a95e5b033776fce80641b5e1fc6c5","tid":2065772,"uid":172051,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:46:06.000Z","msg":"文科唔會易得起邊<br />\n瘋狂paper"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:05:14.000Z","msg":"讀pure math 咪唔洗做lab <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29659da40965796307b1fb501e643ffb307cfd4f","tid":2065772,"uid":155256,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:07:51.000Z","msg":"點讀唔掂都讀左3年 捱埋呢1年佢你一定唔會後悔<br />\n<br />\n試下唔好將件事諗到咁mission impossible <br />\n休息下個腦 慢慢黎 冷靜下 <br />\n諗下要pass埋個degree 仲差幾多 仲差要做啲乜<br />\n度個list 出黎話比自己知有咩最minimum 既野要去完成 <br />\n再一樣一樣去搞掂<br />\n你唔諗唔理想去逃避佢個陣恐懼感一定難受過你面對佢幾十倍<br />\n試下洗下塊面 認真面對佢<br />\n可能會發現未必真係咁難解決既<br />\n或者搵下同學/tutor/朋友 傾下"},{"pid":"f805cbe8c1303fa2a849527725c0484bc9c0b930","tid":2065772,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:14:36.0